```csharp
using Pulumi;
using Aiven = Pulumi.Aiven;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var myproject = new Aiven.Project("myproject", new Aiven.ProjectArgs
        {
            CardId = "<FULL_CARD_ID/LAST4_DIGITS>",
            Project = "<PROJECT_NAME>",
        });
    }

}
```
